Class RoomBookingServiceImplementation

java.lang.Object
com.itkolleg.bookingsystem.service.roombooking.RoomBookingServiceImplementation
All Implemented Interfaces:
RoomBookingService
@Service public class RoomBookingServiceImplementation extends Object implements RoomBookingService
The RoomBookingServiceImplementation class is responsible for implementing the RoomBookingService interface and providing the functionality to manage room bookings.
